Class GymOwnerService

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.business.GymOwnerService
All Implemented Interfaces:
GymOwnerInterface
public class GymOwnerService extends Object implements GymOwnerInterface
The `GymOwnerService` class provides the business logic and implementation for gym owner-specific operations, including managing gyms and slots.
